rawContent:
Common signs of #burnout are;

💤 Feeling tired or drained most of the time
🤕 Feeling helpless, trapped, defeated
🥀 Feeling detached or alone in the world 
👎🏻 Having a negative outlook
🤦🏽‍♂️ Self-doubt
🏃🏾‍♀️ Procrastinating
🙍🏽‍♀️ Feeling overwhelmed

Source; #MentalHealth UK

media.altText:
This is an image by @sanapowell.lpc via Instagram. The image is titled "Signs you might need a mental health break"

There is an image of a battery with low energy and around it are the following signs:
- You've been getting sick often.
- You feel overwhelmed and depleted.
- You haven't been able to enjoy things.
- You haven't had much time for yourself.
- Your sleep/nutrition has been poor.
- You feel unmotivated and lethargic.
- You're relying on unhealthy coping skills. 
- You've had trouble focusing on things.
